<div>
  <%= partial 'partials/navbar' %>
</div>
<div>
  <%= partial 'partials/banner' %>
</div>

<div class="container my-5">
  <div id="projects">
    <h1 class="roboto-bold" style="color: white; margin-bottom: 20px;">Recent Projects</h1>

    <!-- About Section -->
    <%= partial 'partials/about' %>

    <div class="card-container">
      <div class="card-products">
        <div class="card-product">
          <a href="#" class="project-image">
            <%= image_tag 'projects/Plans-Tonight-Show-1.png', alt: 'Plans Tonight', class: 'image' %>
          </a>
          <div class="card-trip-infos">
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
              <h2>Plans Tonight</h2>
              <a class="btn btn-ghost roboto-regular" href="#">Mobile App</a>
            </div>
            <p>Plans Tonight was the final project for Le Wagon Tokyo's 9-week intensive coding bootcamp. This app is designed to reduce the headache of choosing a date and time, invite friends to vote for the mood and alcohol type they prefer. Based on these choices, the app will decide on a bar for you!</p>
            <p>2 Weeks</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card-product">
          <a href="#" class="project-image">
            <%= image_tag 'projects/Kollab-Gradient-BK.png', alt: 'Kollab', class: 'image' %>
          </a>
          <div class="card-trip-infos">
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
              <h2>Kollab</h2>
              <a class="btn btn-ghost roboto-regular" href="#">Web Page</a>
            </div>
            <h3>Role: Lead Developer</h3>
            <p>Kollab was another project where the main focus was to create a collaborative platform. Features include real-time communication and integration with various services.</p>
            <p>1 Week</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <%= partial 'partials/social' %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
